phenomenon, I actually

00:01:09.850 --> 00:01:11.510 align:middle line:84%
was working on
them 40 years ago.

00:01:11.510 --> 00:01:13.750 align:middle line:84%
And the significance
about the work

00:01:13.750 --> 00:01:15.450 align:middle line:84%
on cloning these
cells was I started

00:01:15.450 --> 00:01:18.560 align:middle line:84%
to recognize that they didn't
really necessarily correspond

00:01:18.560 --> 00:01:21.200 align:middle line:84%
to the beliefs that I
was teaching about how

00:01:21.200 --> 00:01:23.460 align:middle line:90%
cells worked in medical school.

00:01:23.460 --> 00:01:25.390 align:middle line:84%
So there was this
disconnect where

00:01:25.390 --> 00:01:27.970 align:middle line:84%
I saw them behaving in
ways that were aberrant,

00:01:27.970 --> 00:01:29.630 align:middle line:90%
or out of the ordinary.

00:01:29.630 --> 00:01:32.080 align:middle line:84%
