out what was going on,

00:01:32.080 --> 00:01:35.020 align:middle line:84%
and what was the difference or
the discrepancy between what

00:01:35.020 --> 00:01:38.130 align:middle line:84%
I expected them to be doing
and what they were doing.

00:01:38.130 --> 00:01:40.220 align:middle line:84%
