that actually hearkens back

00:01:48.970 --> 00:01:51.390 align:middle line:84%
to my first day of
culturing cells,

00:01:51.390 --> 00:01:53.710 align:middle line:84%
my very first experiment
with culturing cells.

00:01:53.710 --> 00:01:57.639 align:middle line:84%
